To compile use:
g++ -Wall -o brickwall BrickBond.cpp BrickWall.cpp main.cpp
or with debug code
g++ -Wall -DDEBUG -o brickwall BrickBond.cpp BrickWall.cpp main.cpp

To Run.

./brickwall 48 10

